WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
The climate of Abu Dhabi is hot and arid. In the summer, 

00:08.000 --> 00:16.000
temperatures average above 35 degrees Celsius and humidity is high. In the 

00:16.000 --> 00:24.000
winter, average temperatures range between 18 and 25 degrees Celsius. There is 

00:24.000 --> 00:32.000
very little rainfall, as it is a desert. 

